        "template--18850231484751__f5332588-ee9e-4cb8-b588-7497ef23f2f0-16824067253affbd63-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Get stuff done<\/strong><\/p><p>And by ‚Äòstuff‚Äô we mean that one huge jaw-dropping¬†<strong>product development project¬†<\/strong>we can‚Äôt reveal just yet. Or the multiple smaller incremental ones we have coming up. Curious? Great, just the quality we‚Äôre looking for in a product developer. Either way, the development of it is yours to plan, manage and fully own. From¬†<strong>conceptualization¬†<\/strong>and‚ÄØ<strong>prototyping‚ÄØ¬†<\/strong>down to‚ÄØ<strong>user testing‚ÄØ¬†<\/strong>and¬†<strong>finetuning¬†<\/strong>the‚ÄØdesign. Your itch to organize things? Here‚Äôs where you get to scratch it.<\/p><p><strong>Play the team card<\/strong><\/p><p>Your negotiating and motivating skills, are they any good? Yes? Great, because you‚Äôre not just working with our own¬†<strong>designers¬†<\/strong>and¬†<strong>engineers<\/strong>. You also follow up on the external acoustic engineers and suppliers involved. In short: you plug in the right people at the right time. No need to show you the ropes though, you have an eye for¬†<strong>detail¬†<\/strong>and a knack for understanding what needs to be done. You have the experience, and you‚Äôre not afraid to use it. Oh, and if you do need a second pair of eyes, just touch base with Robrecht, our Product Development Manager, or Sander your team lead.<\/p><p>Speaking of¬†<strong>teams<\/strong>. You won‚Äôt be doing this alone. Far from. We want to double the development team in the next three months. From nine to twenty Loopers. Yes, we‚Äôre ambitious. But you are too, right?<\/p>",
            "description_padding": 32
          }
        },
        "82ff3a37-8cad-430f-95db-9cbdeeef6ec9": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Requirements",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "32a98dbe-f634-469b-8904-0f5d2149e699": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Only three of them? Yes. Nice surprise, isn‚Äôt it? They‚Äôre not up for discussion though. Must-have material.<\/p><ul><li>You know how to get your ideas across. You‚Äôre¬†<strong>fluent in English, both written and spoken.<\/strong><\/li><li>You‚Äôre pretty awesome in general. A sense of humor? Even better.<\/li><li>You‚Äôre¬†<strong>in our Antwerp office on a regular basis<\/strong>, but otherwise you‚Äôre¬†<strong>free to work wherever<\/strong>. Why? You need to work with a lot of other Loopers on a hardware product. And that‚Äôs just easier in person.<\/li><\/ul>",
